<1ST_LINE>u f AM-WallStreet 2ndLd-Writethru   02-16 0563</1ST_LINE>
<2ND_LINE>AM-Wall Street, 2nd Ld-Writethru,0586</2ND_LINE>
<NOTE>Eds: Inserts 1 graf after 11th graf, Big Board ..., to include
advancing and declining issues; picks up 12th graf pvs, Firestone
